genresAdvancedInfo.name: swedish jazz orkester
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Swedish jazz orkester, or Swedish jazz orchestra, is a larger ensemble that typically features brass, woodwind, and percussion instruments. These orchestras often perform arrangements of popular jazz standards, as well as original compositions by Swedish jazz composers. The result is a rich, full sound that showcases the talents of multiple musicians working together in harmony.
